"children":"Internal privacy management for non-technical teams"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-surface rounded-xl p-5","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold mb-2","children":"Use Codepliant + Termly or Iubenda together when you need"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"text-sm text-muted space-y-1 list-disc list-inside","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Code-based compliance documentation plus a managed cookie consent banner"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Full-stack compliance: documents from Codepliant, consent UX from a consent platform"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Multi-framework compliance (SOC 2, HIPAA, AI Act) alongside cookie consent management"}]]}]]}]]}]]}]
7:["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6","children":"Why developers choose Codepliant"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-6 text-base text-muted leading-relaxed","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground pt-2","children":"Accuracy from code, not memory"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When you fill out a form builder, you are working from memory. Do you remember every analytics SDK in your package.json? Every environment variable that connects to a third-party service? Every database field that stores personal data? Codepliant scans all of this automatically. In benchmark testing across 100 open source repositories, Codepliant achieved 97.8% detection precision for data practices."}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground pt-2","children":"35+ document types vs 5"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Termly and Iubenda generate privacy policies, terms of service, cookie policies, and consent banners — approximately five document types. Codepliant generates 35+ document types covering GDPR (privacy policy, DPA, DSAR guide, DPIA, data flow map), SOC 2 (readiness checklist, control mapping, gap analysis), HIPAA (risk assessment, BAA, PHI detection report), and the EU AI Act (AI disclosure, model inventory, risk assessment)."}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground pt-2","children":"Continuous compliance via CI/CD"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Termly and Iubenda documents are static — they reflect what you entered in the form at a point in time. As your application evolves, your compliance documents drift from reality. Codepliant integrates into your CI/CD pipeline so documents regenerate on every deployment. New analytics SDK? It appears in your next privacy policy. New AI integration? Your AI disclosure updates automatically."}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground pt-2","children":"Open source and self-hosted"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Codepliant runs entirely on your machine. Your code never leaves your environment. For companies with strict data security requirements — which is most companies that need SOC 2 or HIPAA compliance — this is a significant advantage over cloud-based tools that require you to describe your application to a third-party service."}]]}]]}]
